URL: https://github.com/xdanaux/moderncv

******************************************************************************

This is an extendend and improved version

* added "\dateinfo" section to add a date to your CV (\dateinfo{current as of \monthname, \the\year} will add the current date)
* added "words" package to utilize words instead of icons
* added a way to include a title for the homepage
* fixed warnings about file included
* fixed few typos
* added "\infoiconbold" and "\infotextbold", appending false or true you will get respectively info text/icon bold or info text/icon not bold
* added extra tags to pdf generation

Author: Michele Porelli <linux571@gmail.com>